# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OS files
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Python / test tooling
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
.pytest_cache/
# pytest.ini is a local-only test config for this template repo
# (target projects ship their own).
pytest.ini
# Inside tests/: track only files whose name starts with "test_".
tests/*
!tests/test_*
!tests/conftest.py
!tests/_diff_render_runner.js
!tests/_split_tree_runner.js
!tests/_canvas_bus_runner.js

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AI workflow — per-project mutable working file
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# project.yaml is filled in per project (bootstrap). It must NOT be tracked in
# this template repo: a tracked file gets reverted to its committed contents on
# every branch-switch/merge/checkout, silently wiping the bootstrap fill. The
# blank skeleton ships as the tracked .ai/project.yaml.template (installers copy
# it to a target's working .ai/project.yaml). models.yaml stays tracked — its
# committed defaults are useful as-is.
.ai/project.yaml

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AI workflow — generated content
# Track these directories as empty folders (via .gitkeep);
# ignore everything generated inside them.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.ai/plans/*
.ai/specs/*
# Agent Council run records (the council writes runtime here; the other former
# runtime dirs moved under .ai/local/ in the structure overhaul).
.ai/council/runs/*
!.ai/council/runs/.gitkeep
!.ai/plans/.gitkeep
!.ai/specs/.gitkeep

# The .agents/skills/ mirror is GENERATED from .claude/skills/ by
# .ai/scripts/sync_skills.py (and by the installers' mirror loop). It is
# byte-identical to .claude/skills/ for the 10 shared skills, so we don't
# version it. The one exception is the cross-tool bridge `claude/`, which has
# NO .claude/skills/ source — it is its own source of truth, so it stays tracked.
.agents/skills/*
!.agents/skills/claude/
!.agents/skills/claude/**

# Eval harness run outputs: arm-*.jsonl and archived runs are regenerated per
# run (machine-specific timings, transient). The curated record lives in
# .ai/eval/ABLATION.md; .gitkeep preserves results/ and results/proposals/.
.ai/eval/results/*
!.ai/eval/results/.gitkeep
!.ai/eval/results/proposals/
.ai/eval/results/proposals/*
!.ai/eval/results/proposals/.gitkeep

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AI workflow — local / per-developer files
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Generated runtime data lives under .ai/local/. The known runtime dirs are
# tracked as empty folders (.gitkeep) so they exist on a fresh clone; their
# generated contents are ignored. Anything else under .ai/local/ is ignored
# too (catch-all for ad-hoc local / per-developer files).
.ai/local/*
!.ai/local/ledgers/
!.ai/local/agent-runs/
!.ai/local/pipelines/
!.ai/local/jobs/
!.ai/local/proposals/
.ai/local/ledgers/*
!.ai/local/ledgers/.gitkeep
.ai/local/agent-runs/*
!.ai/local/agent-runs/.gitkeep
.ai/local/pipelines/*
!.ai/local/pipelines/.gitkeep
.ai/local/jobs/*
!.ai/local/jobs/.gitkeep
.ai/local/proposals/*
!.ai/local/proposals/agents/
!.ai/local/proposals/skills/
!.ai/local/proposals/skill_backups/
.ai/local/proposals/agents/*
!.ai/local/proposals/agents/.gitkeep
.ai/local/proposals/skills/*
!.ai/local/proposals/skills/.gitkeep
.ai/local/proposals/skill_backups/*
!.ai/local/proposals/skill_backups/.gitkeep
.ai/dashboard/.server-*.log
.ai/dashboard/.server-*.err
# Per-session runtime lock files written by the dashboard session engine.
.ai/dashboard/sessions/

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Local-only repo extras (not shipped via install.sh, not pushed)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Local reference docs (design-system / superpowers mirror + ad-hoc notes)
/docs/
# Scratch directories
/tmp/
/assets/
# Workflow script testbed (install.sh / update-workflow.sh integration tests)
/test-env/
/.githooks/
.github/*
!.github/assets/
.github/assets/*
!.github/assets/diagrams/
!.github/assets/diagrams/**
!.github/assets/screenshots/
!.github/assets/screenshots/**

.ai/qa-screens/
.superpowers/
.ai/reviews/
# git worktrees (isolated workspaces)
.worktrees/